title: Vivaldi - Six Cello Sonatas - Hogwood, AAM, Coin
description:
Vivaldi: Six Cello Sonatas.

This perfect CD, by far my favourite chamber music recording for 20 years now, features six Cello Sonatas composed by Antonio Vivaldi. The disc features the following performers:

Christophe Coin, Cello
Christopher Hogwood, Harpsichord
Ageet Zweistra, Cello
Eugene Ferre, Baroque Guitar
Tom Finucane, Archlute

It was released by L'Oiseau Lyre in 1989.

Please do yourself the favour of listening to this perfect music.

MP3 @ 320
